the National Science Foundation, the Department of Energy, the National 
Aeronautics and Space Administration, and the University Corporation for 
Atmospheric Research's National Center for Atmospheric Research.

Except for the segregable components listed below, CCSM is public domain 
software.  There may be other third party tools and libraries that are 
embedded, and they may have their own copyright notices and terms.

The following components are copyrighted and may only be used, modified, or 
redistributed under the terms indicated below.

